: 69, "seek": 20216, "start": 202.16, "end": 204.04, "text": " And that's pretty much it.", "tokens": [50364, 400, 300, 311, 1238, 709, 309, 13, 50458], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.13011189415341332, "compression_ratio": 1.5594713656387664, "no_speech_prob": 0.00023178545234259218}, {"id": 70, "seek": 20216, "start": 204.04, "end": 209.04, "text": " Now, if you want to, at the end of the workshop feedback,", "tokens": [50458, 823, 11, 498, 291, 528, 281, 11, 412, 264, 917, 295, 264, 13541, 5824, 11, 50708], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.13011189415341332, "compression_ratio": 1.5594713656387664, "no_speech_prob": 0.00023178545234259218}, {"id": 71, "seek": 20216, "start": 209.04, "end": 213.12, "text": " what this does is I wrote a logic or Claude did", "tokens": [50708, 437, 341, 775, 307, 286, 4114, 257, 9952, 420, 12947, 2303, 630, 50912], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.13011189415341332, "compression_ratio": 1.5594713656387664, "no_speech_prob": 0.00023178545234259218}, {"id": 72, "seek": 20216, "start": 214.32, "end": 215.96, "text": " so that it can do two things.", "tokens": [50972, 370, 300, 309, 393, 360, 732, 721, 13, 51054], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.13011189415341332, "compression_ratio": 1.5594713656387664, "no_speech_prob": 0.00023178545234259218}, {"id": 73, "seek": 20216, "start": 215.96, "end": 218.72, "text": " One, it will give you a feedback", "tokens": [51054, 1485, 11, 309, 486, 976, 291, 257, 5824, 51192], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.13011189415341332, "compression_ratio": 1.5594713656387664, "no_speech_prob": 0.00023178545234259218}, {"id": 74, "seek": 20216, "start": 218.72, "end": 221.28, "text": " based on your session files", "tokens": [51192, 2361, 322, 428, 5481, 7098, 51320], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.13011189415341332, "compression_ratio": 1.5594713656387664, "no_speech_prob": 0.00023178545234259218}, {"id": 75, "seek": 20216, "start": 221.28, "end": 223.28, "text": " on where you're doing well", "tokens": [51320, 322, 689, 291, 434, 884, 731, 51420], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.13011189415341332, "compression_ratio": 1.5594713656387664, "no_speech_prob": 0.00023178545234259218}, {"id": 76, "seek": 20216, "start": 223.28, "end": 225.2, "text": " and where you would need to improve.", "tokens": [51420, 293, 689, 291, 576, 643, 281, 3470, 13, 51516], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.13011189415341332, "compression_ratio": 1.5594713656387664, "no_speech_prob": 0.00023178545234259218}, {"id": 77, "seek": 20216, "start": 225.2, "end": 226.48, "text": " That means you haven't got to keep going back", "tokens": [51516, 663, 1355, 291, 2378, 380, 658, 281, 1066, 516, 646, 51580], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.13011189415341332, "compression_ratio": 1.5594713656387664, "no_speech_prob": 0.00023178545234259218}, {"id": 78, "seek": 20216, "start": 226.48, "end": 227.4, "text": " through the modules.", "tokens": [51580, 807, 264, 16679, 13, 51626], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.13011189415341332, "compression_ratio": 1.5594713656387664, "no_speech_prob": 0.00023178545234259218}, {"id": 79, "seek": 22740, "start": 228.4, "end": 233.08, "text": " Secondly, the other is you can run a diagnostics", "tokens": [50414, 19483, 11, 264, 661, 307, 291, 393, 1190, 257, 43215, 1167, 50648], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12672876603532546, "compression_ratio": 1.614678899082569, "no_speech_prob": 0.0011500698747113347}, {"id": 80, "seek": 22740, "start": 233.08, "end": 235.0, "text": " and then you can give that to me.", "tokens": [50648, 293, 550, 291, 393, 976, 300, 281, 385, 13, 50744], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12672876603532546, "compression_ratio": 1.614678899082569, "no_speech_prob": 0.0011500698747113347}, {"id": 81, "seek": 22740, "start": 235.0, "end": 239.92000000000002, "text": " Now, because this is not only self drive itself improving,", "tokens": [50744, 823, 11, 570, 341, 307, 406, 787, 2698, 333